Westport Bancorp Inc said itdeclared a 100 pct stock dividend and increased the quarterlycash dividend.    The company said the the stock dividend, to effect atwo-for-one stock split, is payable July six to holders ofrecord June 12.    It said the dividend on present shares was increased to 26cts, from 25 cts in the prior quarter, payable July one toholders of record June 12. Reuter&#3;